{"tid":1906221,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武球王（牙武）傳中製造烏龍球之後 班支那人又玻璃心發作","createTime":"2020-03-01T19:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T05:23:46.000Z","uid":234509,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb952ece7705106a6510c52b8892f0997ef2ebcf","tid":1906221,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:07:40.000Z","msg":"馬體會對愛斯賓奴嘅比賽入面<br />\n支那球王武磊傳中搞到savic擺烏龍<br />\n搶點嘅11號球員RDT以為係自己入波跟住就鏟草<br />\n點知原來係烏龍球<br />\n球隊入波開心點都係正常<br />\n但唔知點解班支那人玻璃心上去愛支賓奴ig爆閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話咩佢地只係為咗睇武磊唔係睇隊波<br />\n認真 武磊踢波球品人品冇咩問題<br />\n亞洲球員嚟講算幾勁<br />\n但佢班支那fans真係影衰晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXz68DH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXz68DH.gif&h=bfd3665e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRUx3h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRUx3h.png&h=9e370e8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce37a59f560e5959a285e1dce44e07001375c1c9","tid":1906221,"uid":147367,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"支那人既事關我撚事，佢哋鍾意出醜咪出醜"},{"pid":"507d5202ddfb7e9640db7ef89999b550c05aad66","tid":1906221,"uid":234509,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce37a59f560e5959a285e1dce44e07001375c1c9","tid":1906221,"uid":147367,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"支那人既事關我撚事，佢哋鍾意出醜咪出醜"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔關你事入嚟做咩<br />\n做attention seeker好型？"},{"pid":"5a3065f50d64f857fc1d00c115d2bd2573db70a8","tid":1906221,"uid":306576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"507d5202ddfb7e9640db7ef89999b550c05aad66","tid":1906221,"uid":234509,"like":10,"dislike":10,"sc